though stanford's servers support for assistance please contact your local help desk for the medical school call 5 8000 for non medical school users please submit a helpsu request or dial 5 help rates free of charge getting started using the service is easy all you need to do is put secure somewhere in the subject line of the message last modified wed 6 jul 2011 at 16 43 pages about this service overview sending secure email receiving secure email registering for secure email secure email with forwarded accounts resetting your password secure email for gsb faculty staff and students how secure email works retrieving email from the old secure email servers find answers submit a helpsu request secure email faq related pages secure computing classification of data guidelines for securing mobile computing devices configuring your email program footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
